---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<Layout title="Post Heart Attack Follow-up — Dr Delhasse" description="Recovery and cardiological follow-up after myocardial infarction. Recurrence prevention with Dr Delhasse." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{label:'Home', href:'/en'}, {label:'Areas of Expertise', href:'/en/areas-of-expertise'}, {label:'Post Heart Attack Follow-up'}]} />
      <h1>Post Heart Attack <span class="text-primary">Follow-up</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Recovery starts here</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/detail/suivi-post-infarctus.webp" alt="Post heart attack follow-up" class="detail-hero-img" />
      <img src="/images/svg/expertise/Suivi-apres-infarctus.svg" alt="Post heart attack follow-up" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>After a heart attack, recovery depends on the extent of damage to the heart, particularly the left ventricle's ability to pump blood effectively.</p>

      <p>Emergency coronary angiography improves immediate survival but does not treat the underlying disease, requiring long-term treatment. Medications include aspirin for blood thinning, antihypertensives and blood sugar treatments if necessary.</p>

      <p>Lifestyle changes are essential: a suitable diet, regular physical activity, smoking cessation and optimal management of hypertension, diabetes and cholesterol.</p>

      <p>Regular cardiology consultations allow follow-up and treatment adjustment. This follow-up combined with lifestyle changes reduces the risk of complications and improves quality of life.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/areas-of-expertise" class="btn btn--outline-dark">&larr; All areas</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-hero-img { width: 100%; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
